Canonical website:
  http://www.abisource.com/

Canonical download:
  http://www.abisource.com/downloads/abiword/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack abiword-2.8.1-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./abiword-2.8.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/abiword-2.8.1-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/abiword-2.8.1-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/abiword-plugins-2.8.1-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libabiword2.8-2.8.1-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libabiword2.8-devel-2.8.1-X.tar.bz2

